      "title": "User Acceptance Testing",
      "subtitle": "Business Validation Before Go-Live"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "System Integration Testing has been successfully completed. The project now enters User Acceptance Testing (UAT), where actual business users validate that SAP TM supports their daily transportation operations. Unlike SIT, business users-not consultants-decide whether the solution meets operational expectations."
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC3",
